SYNOPSIS

    In your weaver.ini:

     [-WordList]

DESCRIPTION

    This plugin is to be used when building WordList::* distribution.
    Currently it does the following:

      * Add a Synopsis section (it doesn't already exist) showing how to
      use the module

      * Add Statistics section showing statistics from %STATS (which can be
      generated by DZP:WordList)

SEE ALSO

    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::WordList

